#pragma omp parallel copyin(x, y)  \n   {  \n      x = y;  \n   }  \n}  \n```  \n  \n Possible resolution:  \n  \n```  \n// C3053b.cpp  \n// compile with: /openmp /LD  \nint x, y;  \n#pragma omp threadprivate(x, y)  \n  \nvoid Test() {  \n   #pragma omp parallel copyin(x, y)  \n   {  \n      x = y;  \n   }  \n}  \n```"}